## Tile.frameNumLastRequested property

Keeping some stats for the individual \[\[Tile\]\]s to analyze caching behavior.

The frame the \[\[Tile\]\] was last requested. This is required to know when the given \[\[Tile\]\] can be removed from the cache.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
frameNumLastRequested: number;
```
